## Backup & Restore Status Matrix

### Backup Types
| Type | Scope | Who Can Trigger |
|------|-------|-----------------|
| Tenant Backup | Single tenant | Tenant Admin, Super Admin |
| Full Backup | All tenants | Super Admin only |
| Scheduled Backup | Per configuration | Automated |

### Backup Permissions
| Action | Tenant Admin | Super Admin |
|--------|--------------|-------------|
| View own tenant backups | ✅ | ✅ |
| View all tenant backups | ❌ | ✅ |
| Trigger tenant backup | ✅ | ✅ |
| Trigger full system backup | ❌ | ✅ |
| Modify backup schedule | ✅ (own tenant) | ✅ (global) |
| Delete backup | ❌ | ✅ |
| Request restore | ❌ (requires approval) | ✅ (requires second approval) |
| Approve restore | ❌ | ✅ (second Super Admin) |

### Backup Status
- `Queued` - Waiting to run
- `Running` - Currently executing
- `Succeeded` - Completed successfully
- `Failed` - Execution error
- `VerificationFailed` - Backup created but verification failed

## Database Baseline Rules

### Required Fields for Every Table
- `id uuid PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid()`
- `created_at timestamptz NOT NULL DEFAULT now()`
- `updated_at timestamptz`
- `is_active boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT true`
- `tenant_id uuid REFERENCES tenants(id)` (if tenant-scoped)

### Index Requirements
- All foreign keys MUST have indexes
- `tenant_id` MUST be indexed on tenant-scoped tables
- `created_at` SHOULD be indexed for time-based query paths

### Migration Rules
- NEVER delete columns directly; mark as `is_deleted` or `deprecated`
- NEVER modify existing migration files after they are committed
- Use additive schema changes only (new columns, new tables)
- Perform data backfill in separate migration/step from schema introduction

## Frontend-Admin (FA) Specific Rules

### Page Structure (Reference)
```text
src/app/(protected)/
├── admin/
│   ├── users/page.tsx
│   ├── tenants/[id]/page.tsx
│   ├── backup/page.tsx
│   └── reports/page.tsx
├── dashboard/page.tsx
└── profile/page.tsx
```

### Component Organization (Reference)
```text
src/features/
├── users/
│   ├── components/
│   │   ├── UsersTable.tsx
│   │   ├── CreateUserModal.tsx
│   │   ├── EditUsernameModal.tsx
│   │   └── UserDetailCard.tsx
│   ├── api/
│   │   └── userHooks.ts
│   └── pages/
│       └── UserListPage.tsx
```

### State Management
- Use TanStack Query for server state
- Use Zustand for client state (theme, UI preferences)
- NEVER store sensitive data in Zustand

## Frontend-POS (FE) Specific Rules

### Offline Support
- Use IndexedDB/PouchDB for offline storage
- Queue offline transactions in `pendingPaymentQueue`
- Sync queued records when network connection is restored
- NEVER store plain-text voucher codes offline

### Device Integration
- Integrate TSE via fiskaly API
- Supported printers: `EPSON TM-T88VI`, `Star TSP 700`
- Use `OCRA-B` font on receipts
- Use camera-based scanner for barcode/QR workflows

### POS Routes (Reference)
```text
app/(tabs)/
├── index.tsx          # Cart/Checkout
├── products.tsx       # Product catalog
├── customers.tsx      # Customer management
├── reports.tsx        # Daily reports
└── profile.tsx        # User settings
```
